targets.expr: sum(rate(storage_api_http_request_duration_seconds_sum{tenant_id=~"$tenant_id"}[$__interval])) by (le, route, method, tenant_id) / sum(rate(storage_api_http_request_duration_seconds_count{tenant_id=~"$tenant_id"}[$__interval])) by (le, route, method, tenant_id)
